description: I realized that I missed one note in measure 23 in my last revision that fixed the issues in the tab that is currently on this site. It is all fixed now
title: My Neighbor Totoro - Path Of The Wind

description:
In measure 23 there was an extra note on the second beat (3rd fret on G string right before the 5th fret on the b string and after the open note on the D string). 
This required that I lengthen the last open note on the G string in the 28th fret in order for the 29th fret to start correctly.
